org.apache.hupa.widgets.editor.bundles
Interface ToolbarImages

All Superinterfaces:
com.google.gwt.resources.client.ClientBundle
public interface ToolbarImages
extends com.google.gwt.resources.client.ClientBundle

This ClientBundle is used for all the button icons. Using an image bundle allows all of these images to be packed into a single image, which saves a lot of HTTP requests, drastically improving startup time.
